Combine coleslaw mix, celery and Dressing; set aside. Combine Lipton(R) Recipe Secrets(R) Onion Soup Mix, ground beef and cayenne pepper sauce; shape into 16 patties. Grill or broil burgers, turning once, 12 minutes or until done. Arrange burgers on rolls, then top with coleslaw. Serve, if desired, with additional cayenne pepper sauce.